能仲細 或者慣左機械式訓練 感情真喺唔多"},{"pid":"ba642859e6be489863ecf81efaf1c75b57a5454a","tid":286941,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"佢老豆好似係咩歌唱教授<br />\n叫譚順生<br />\n最近仲出左翻唱碟<br />\n聽佢唱上海灘真係嚇親我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5cfeab19629c538955dc7d379090930a0d7700","tid":286941,"uid":121744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:46:20.000Z","msg":"老豆係共狗黎<br />\n<br />\n條𡃁妹之前都好出名啦"},{"pid":"3127b8a96fc9a176114b855e3946a4502b398a9b","tid":286941,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登同台下觀眾就係中外文化差異既寫照<br />\n外國你唱得好就一定讚<br />\n香港傳統意想唔讚得 驚人囂<br />\n唱得好都搵野彈下<br />\n槍打出頭鳥<br />\n低質</blockquote><br />\nd父母都係呀<br />\n咩都係挑缺點嚟睇<br />\n心態係想你改進"},{"pid":"c1db28b875aed58160a16a13d0942ccce4fd2363","tid":286941,"uid":29721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:48:09.000Z","msg":"原來係Dr. Steve個女"},{"pid":"cb1b71dce438792bd968f618c6054a50676f1fde","tid":286941,"uid":45817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:49:07.000Z","msg":"係幾好，但完全唔覺有咩咁特色<br />\n吹大左"},{"pid":"701364344e0facc70ae98be409b2d8003682a556","tid":286941,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"起左雞皮<br />\n雖然巴聲唔好聽<br />\n但唱功好勁<br />\n有前途"},{"pid":"e062a6ccd4453507ba7424d5a7801ab4ad710409","tid":286941,"uid":48321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個節目唔係要美國護照做美國人先上得咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔駛架,有一季有個日本仔上去拿埋冠軍"},{"pid":"91cfa065b8916264eb8fbcfc6a49d448af5adf38","tid":286941,"uid":10141,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:49:20.000Z","msg":"聽完我都震驚咗<br />\n<br />\n可以係咁多人面前，外國人面前，攝影機面前都咁有自信，發揮到咁好<br />\n<br />\n香港有幾多個大人夠膽，仲好意思踩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔識欣賞仲係到屌屌屌，只係顯露緊自己心態有幾咁醜陋<br />\n<br />\n以為比負面評價就顯得自己與別不同"},{"pid":"e52943b25ec319800cfe3fede5b5e8dc690f2765","tid":286941,"uid":18220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Connie正好多</blockquote><br />\n根本兩個級數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽呢個小妹妹唱我剩係得好聽既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但connie唱rainbow嗰陣係真係有起雞皮，覺得好似唱入心入面既感覺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCeline頂盡有實力<br />\n但果時既Connie直頭係天使之音<br />\nAmanda次次喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽過Connie會覺得Celine無乜特別"},{"pid":"ffa8fd3995380cb8f9330e68ed4af997a074d013","tid":286941,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"咁的確係幾好聽既<br />\n不過好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂唔順<br />\n同埋佢老豆果陣上東鳩閪望一家人假撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94df1f0db36c2236b682bd00cd183c4659a6692","tid":286941,"uid":18220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"搞清楚<br />\n有實力唔一定好聽<br />\nGEM就係最好例子 (當然佢本身d歌都係7)"},{"pid":"b149293f565245871028dbc32d4827237073f4d3","tid":286941,"uid":18863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"佢膽量同埋應對比好多9歲細路都好得多<br />\n第一次聽我都覺得佢唱得幾好聽<br />\n但聽多幾次 就可以留意到其實佢真喺無咩感情<br />\n估計佢喺屋企唱咗1000次都有 仲要佢老豆會喺佢一邊唱個陣 執佢發音 高低音個啲 先會有咁「完美」嘅表現<br />\n但喺完美嘅技巧同埋聲線唔足夠打動人心<br />\n技巧同聲音只喺你詮釋歌曲嘅工具<br />\n而首歌嘅內容同埋你嘅情感先喺首歌嘅意義"},{"pid":"13cb3409de833f2caa8d3c10097502fe19833460","tid":286941,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"認真無乜特別<br />\n唔係你地講到曉飛咁勁<br />\n普通一個人都可以唱到同佢差唔多<br />\n不話對答如流果下反而要讚下"},{"pid":"a8cbb406b206972c34c4b862e0373243595d5c91","tid":286941,"uid":10194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:22:21.000Z","msg":"香港人係咪讚下人都咁難？"},{"pid":"8daa22294ad2b628301b36ee0c27d940de06faf9","tid":286941,"uid":56620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實好普通，<br />\n呢啲隔硬CHOK 大人聲好難頂</blockquote><br />\n咁你上去唱囉垃圾。人地9歲細路女唱得咁好都要踩。你冇撚用㗎喇，死撚咗佢啦。唔講仲以為你係天王巨星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登真係多得唔少你呢d垃圾</blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講下自己感受都要屌<br />\n9歲又點 覺得普通都要夾硬讚到上天?<br />\n話酸既有咩值得酸 ? <br />\n香港真係多得唔少你地<br />\n永遠講真說話都要比人屌<br />\n結果個個扮道德撚 企哂道德高地<br />\n結果關愛座批鬥呢d咪因為你地先出現</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地罵坐關愛座既人都係真說話咋喎<br />\n講下自己感受都要畀你班連登仔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5892f2f9d0791de7796abd11fd1857ddd149f669","tid":286941,"uid":18271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢老豆係歌唱老師黎 細個已經不停train個女<br />\n就咁睇條片 第一下我都覺得好聽嘅<br />\n但係聽耐左 同呀GEM鳩叫一樣 無感情<br />\n個細路仔去AGT之前已經參加過好多中國show<br />\n好似係國慶晚會有請佢黎唱<br />\n老實講 唔係想踩底佢<br />\n而係奶共嘅細路女 要我讚佢? 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9歲細路女撚識分咩叫奶共<br />\n老豆老母叫就要去架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真係典型痴撚線憤青嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d7d0ab611cb65808bbcbfc5d420a77fb8fc017","tid":286941,"uid":58219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽完我都震驚咗<br />\n<br />\n可以係咁多人面前，外國人面前，攝影機面前都咁有自信，發揮到咁好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港有幾多個大人夠膽，仲好意思踩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n唔識欣賞仲係到屌屌屌，只係顯露緊自己心態有幾咁醜陋<br />\n<br />\n以為比負面評價就顯得自己與別不同</blockquote><br />\n呢個時候班友就會話&quot;講馬洗唔洗跑得快過隻馬先有資格呀?&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c41d7a141665d92bfc706f492639961e5c0b9f4","tid":286941,"uid":59753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"唔好話佢唱成點 9歲黎講當住一班外國人面前上台表演剩係果份自信台型已經好難得 就算你話佢之前上過其它節目有類似經驗都咁話 你諗下你9歲果時做緊乜 我自問19歲果時都無佢果份自信"},{"pid":"ccee31150c5b28bd6b2a0f75ae196bfdfee6fe85","tid":286941,"uid":67895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔9歲個陣做緊咩？</blockquote><br />\n你唔計埋人地老豆老母洗幾多錢落佢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窮撚有天份都冇用啦，冇錢<br />\n冇錢咪落公園玩泥沙囉<br />\n有咩可以做"},{"pid":"a18b8c4ab385c72bc04b9d75b1ae13e2a614e166","tid":286941,"uid":18220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好話佢唱成點 9歲黎講當住一班外國人面前上台表演剩係果份自信台型已經好難得 就算你話佢之前上過其它節目有類似經驗都咁話 你諗下你9歲果時做緊乜 我自問19歲果時都無佢果份自信</blockquote><br />\n當年林昇湋都好有guts<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56164e0680cba84d29c235d62494488707a184d","tid":286941,"uid":14816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實好普通，<br />\n呢啲隔硬CHOK 大人聲好難頂</blockquote><br />\n咁你上去唱囉垃圾。人地9歲細路女唱得咁好都要踩。你冇撚用㗎喇，死撚咗佢啦。唔講仲以為你係天王巨星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登真係多得唔少你呢d垃圾</blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor